Description: Species corresponding to the main characters of Rudyard Kipling's Jungle Book, set in the jungles of India - Akela (Indian wolf), Bagheera (panther), Baloo (sloth bear), Bandar-log (macacques), Chil (Brahminy kite), Hathi (Asian elephant), Kaa (Indian python), Mowgli (human), Rikki-Tikki (Indian mongoose), Shere Kan (Bengal tiger)
